data.description: **PRICE IMPROVEMENT** Opportunity in the St. James Village North Neighborhood!!   Discover the Charm of this Single-Family Home in a Desirable Location! This exceptional property is a hidden gem within the sought-after St. James Village North neighborhood, offering every convenience you desire in a community!  Featuring 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, and a finished basement, this home is a welcoming oasis. As you enter, a two-story foyer with gleaming hardwood floors greets you, setting the stage for what's to come. The open and well-thought-out main floor plan effortlessly flows from the traditional dining/living room space to the semi-open kitchen concept. Abundant windows flood the home with natural light, and the kitchen showcases updated cabinetry and modern appliances.  Upstairs features plush wall-to-wall carpeting leading to an oversized en-suite primary bedroom, complete with a walk-in closet, a luxurious garden bath, double vanity, and a separate shower. Down the hall you’ll find 3 generous size bedrooms and a full size bathroom. The fully finished basement is a hub for entertainment, boasting a spacious family room, a full bath for added convenience, and a bar area that's ideal for hosting gatherings. Whether you're planning a movie night or a celebration, this space has it all! Step outside onto your freshly stained deck, which offers a scenic view of the beautifully maintained backyard, creating an inviting outdoor living space where entertaining opportunities are endless.   We understood the challenge presented by the current interest rates and offered a PRICE IMPROVEMENT to make this home even more appealing to you. Don't let this NEW amazing opportunity pass you by.  Schedule your showing today! Plus, as an added  bonus, the seller will provide a 1-year Eagle Premier First American Home Warranty for your peace of mind. .
